{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be bold and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f4f7fc;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0a4f7a;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        nav {\n            background-color: #005f9a;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 14px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            background-color: #0a4f7a;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            color: #005f9a;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #eef2f7;\n            padding: 25px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid #005f9a;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #005f9a;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #005f9a;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 30px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #0a4f7a;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #0a4f7a;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: #005f9a;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 70px 20px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #005f9a 0%, #0a4f7a 100%);\n        }\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin: 0 0 15px 0;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            line-height: 1.7;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Apex Legal Solutions</h1>\n        <p>Your Trusted Advocates</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h2>Excellence in Legal Representation</h2>\n        <p>Dedicated to providing superior legal counsel and achieving the best outcomes for our clients.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; line-height: 1.7;\">\n            Apex Legal Solutions is a distinguished law firm committed to upholding justice and serving our clients with integrity and expertise.\n            With a team of highly skilled and experienced legal professionals, we offer comprehensive legal services across a wide range of practice areas.\n            Our mission is to provide personalized, effective, and aggressive representation to protect your rights and interests.\n        </p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                <p>Guiding businesses through complex legal landscapes with strategic advice and robust representation.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                <p>Assertive advocacy in all stages of litigation, ensuring your voice is heard in the courtroom.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                <p>Navigating property transactions and disputes with precision and thoroughness.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Family Law</h3>\n                <p>Compassionate and determined representation for sensitive family matters.</p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                <p>Protecting your innovations and creative works with expert legal strategies.</p>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Criminal Defense</h3>\n                <p>Unyielding defense for individuals facing criminal charges.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n        <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n            We are ready to discuss your legal needs. Please fill out the form below or call us directly.\n        </p>\n        <form class=\"contact-form\">\n            <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\" required>\n            <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}